About
=====

This file explains how to compile the console version of primesieve
to compile the Qt GUI version please refer to qt-gui/INSTALL.

How to build primesieve
=======================

Open a terminal or Command Prompt cd into the primesieve directory and
run:

  1. Microsoft Visual C++
     > nmake -f Makefile.msvc

  2. GNU g++
     $ make

  3. Other C++ compilers (icpc, sunCC, llvm-g++, ...)
     $ make CXX=my_compiler

  The above make/nmake command compiles the primesieve binary to ./out

How to test it
==============

  > out\primesieve -help
  Shows usage examples and an option summary.
  
  > out\primesieve -test
  Runs various sieving tests to check if primesieve produces correct
  results.

  NOTE: for Unix-like operating systems use out/./primesieve
